how to add comment to be used by terminal at all : 
mv </bin :which in the dir of tool> /bin/
how to create Database (db):  
mysql -u root -p
CREATE USER 'newuser'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'some_very_complex_password';
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON * . * TO 'newuser'@'localhost';
FLUSH PRIVILEGES;
how to install a tool using snapcraft store like (xmind) : 
site : https://snapcraft.io/xmind 
enable snap : 
sudo apt update
sudo apt install snapd
sudo snap install core 
install : 
sudo snap install xmind 
